title: PAX Aus Skins still not given out?
body: Just would like an update on the Pax Aus skins from this year. I submitted my proof of purchase of the Pax tickets when it was announced that Riot wasn't going to be at Pax, but still haven't received anything or heard anything about it since then.

replies.body: I'm guessing nobody with the relevant information is going to see this post. My suggestion is to submit a [Support Ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and ask, and if you already had one, reopen it.
